      <title>波士顿市长重启推动房主减税计划 应对税费激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/boston-mayor-revives-push-for-homeowner-tax-relief-as-bills-jump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波士顿市长米歇尔吴 (Michelle Wu) 正试图重启一项失败的努力，以减轻因房产税两位数增长而遭受的房主的负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/boston-mayor-revives-push-for-homeowner-tax-relief-as-bills-jump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 16:56:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>小唐纳德·特朗普加入卡尔什并炒作选举投注市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/donald-trump-jr-joins-kalshi-and-hypes-market-for-election-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[小唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump Jr.) 担任预测市场 Kalshi 的顾问，将该博彩网站和其他类似网站打造为评估政治和选举状况的优质来源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/donald-trump-jr-joins-kalshi-and-hypes-market-for-election-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 16:53:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登债务减免计划帮助的学生贷款借款人超过 500 万</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/student-loan-borrowers-aided-by-biden-debt-relief-tops-5-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登周一采取行动，免除超过 15 万人的联邦学生贷款，作为最后一搏，这将使在他执政期间获得贷款减免的借款人总数超过 500 万人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/student-loan-borrowers-aided-by-biden-debt-relief-tops-5-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 16:33:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿克曼支持前对冲基金经理蒂尔森参加纽约市长竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/ackman-backs-ex-hedge-fund-manager-tilson-in-nyc-mayoral-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁比尔·阿克曼表示，他将在激烈的纽约市市长民主党初选中支持前对冲基金经理惠特尼·蒂尔森。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/ackman-backs-ex-hedge-fund-manager-tilson-in-nyc-mayoral-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 16:28:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>艾伯塔省省长警告称，特朗普的关税即将到来，将包括石油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/alberta-premier-warns-trump-tariffs-coming-including-on-oil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿尔伯塔省省长丹尼尔·史密斯在佛罗里达会见美国当选总统后警告称，一旦唐纳德·特朗普下周就任总统，加拿大人应该准备好面对美国关税，石油产品将不会受到豁免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/alberta-premier-warns-trump-tariffs-coming-including-on-oil</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 16:21:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯洛伐克总统菲科提议与泽连斯基会面以恢复天然气供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/slovakia-s-fico-floats-zelenskiy-meeting-on-resuming-gas-transit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年年初，基辅与莫斯科之间的协议到期后，斯洛伐克总理罗伯特·菲佐邀请乌克兰总统弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基就恢复天然气运输进行会谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/slovakia-s-fico-floats-zelenskiy-meeting-on-resuming-gas-transit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 16:10:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟十国表示应制裁俄罗斯天然气和液化天然气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/10-eu-nations-say-it-s-time-to-sanction-russian-natural-gas-lng</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟十国集团正在推动加大对俄罗斯的制裁，对天然气实施进一步限制，并加强对石油价格上限的执行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/10-eu-nations-say-it-s-time-to-sanction-russian-natural-gas-lng</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 15:52:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱尔兰将加强北欧和波罗的海国家联盟，以增强欧盟影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/ireland-to-bolster-nordic-baltics-alliance-to-gain-eu-clout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普政府上台，都柏林与美国的关系可能会减弱，而爱尔兰则在欧盟寻找更东部的盟友，以在欧盟中获得更多影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/ireland-to-bolster-nordic-baltics-alliance-to-gain-eu-clout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 15:41:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黎巴嫩任命国际法院院长为受灾国家总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/lebanese-diplomat-secures-majority-vote-for-prime-minister-role</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黎巴嫩外交官纳瓦夫·萨拉姆（Nawaf Salam），前联合国特使、现任国际法院院长，被任命为该国总理，负责组建新政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/lebanese-diplomat-secures-majority-vote-for-prime-minister-role</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 14:15:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默对里夫斯“充满信心”，支持财政规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/starmer-has-full-confidence-in-reeves-stresses-fiscal-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默表示，他对财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯“充满信心”，并强调英国政府将坚持财政规则，以应对英国借贷成本飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/starmer-has-full-confidence-in-reeves-stresses-fiscal-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 13:12:25 GMT</pubDate>
